<div1>
<pb n="0219a" id="I01.0081.0219a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 81</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>雷暉嫗造釋迦像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之一　碑陽" type="其他"/><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a01"/><p id="pI01p0219a0101">大周保定五年歲次乙酉五月
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a02"/>壬午朔五日丙戌。
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a03"/>雷暉嫗者。三門護軍王□之孫。
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a04"/>功曹張郎之女也。父祖相承。<note n="0219001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">閞＝關【史】</note><app n="0219001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【原】">閞</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a05"/>中豪族。歷代酋<note n="0219002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31042;＝望【史】</note><app n="0219002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31042;</rdg></app>。軀雖受女身。
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a06"/>志性真明。殊懷丈夫之<note n="0219003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30535;＝操【史】</note><app n="0219003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">操</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30535;</rdg></app>。五德
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a07"/>六藏。體會而能標女儀婦道。動成
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a08"/>於物軌。年在初笄。從禮而□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a09"/>門□字□□。本是□州河東郡
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a10"/>蒲&CB00095;縣人也。&CB00784;朗令哲。譏會無
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a11"/>方。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">覽</unclear>練<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">眾</unclear>經。內<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">外</unclear>斯朗。於神龜
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a12"/>年中。跨滻河□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">觀</unclear>矚<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">跛</unclear>□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a13"/><app source="0219001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【原】">閞</rdg></app>隴優遊西□□氏慕德因□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a14"/>為親繾綣。一生事同魚□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a15"/>永熙之季。海內□遶魏□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a16"/>英豪岳□□□□方欲<note n="0219004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31043;＝掃【史】</note><app n="0219004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">掃</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31043;</rdg></app>定<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">宇</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a17"/>宙。廣募賢良猛<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">騎</unclear>。時忠勇奮發。□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219a18"/>□□應命。即除龍驤將軍。□□</p>
</div2>
</div1>
<div1>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b00"/><mulu level="1" label="之二　碑側" type="其他"/><head>之二　碑側</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b01"/><p id="pI01p0219b0101">□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□□有壹子。字令業。長成□□□有<note n="0219005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">乂＝父【史】</note><app n="0219005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">父</lem><rdg wit="【原】">乂</rdg></app>風。文經武略。庶
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b02"/>□□□□□□□□□□年中。<note n="0219006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">寑＝寢【史】</note><app n="0219006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">寑</rdg></app>疾而終。凡在親知。愛其父子仁義□□。莫不留戀。嫗<note n="0219007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00517;＝愍【史】</note><app n="0219007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">愍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00517;</rdg></app>之□息
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b03"/>□□□□□□□塗三&CB04020;。三&CB04020;者。天地初開。伏羲之<note n="0219008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30903;＝舊【史】</note><app n="0219008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30903;</rdg></app>名。往古來今。聖賢之所都邑。皆無凶咎。遂
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b04"/>□□父子同<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">埒</unclear>。精靈莫二。其墳上高十尺。下至黃泉。棺槨相重。儭幣自周。蒔柏卅餘□。并諸□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b05"/>有□春<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">冬</unclear>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">變</unclear>。又仰憑　三寶。有濟度之能。敬造釋加石像前後兩堪。并諸聖之像。□□□□□
<lb ed="C I" n="0219b06"/>□。等同斯福。法界含生。□登正道。物之堅固者。莫過金石。署碑於墓。永存．．．</p>
</div2>
</div1>
